% warrants.bib — the claims of paperkit's front-door doc.  This README is itself
% a paperkit projection of THIS file (root paper.toml: out = README.md).  Every
% example is a CITED claim that also emits its on-disk asset (emit = …): the prose
% introduces and cites it [@key], the block renders below it.  An emit with no
% claim would be an UNCITED placement — a postulate — so there are none here.

